ability.name: Paseo por el Bosque

ability.name: Circo Aéreo

attacks.name: Esquirla al Viento

ability.name: Camuflaje Forestal

attacks.name: Flecha Dividida

attacks.name: Anclaje Ira

attacks.name: Gigamartillo

attacks.name: Cadena Oscilante

name: Bolifacio

name: Entrenador de Gimnasio

name: Escudo Oxidado

name: Rose

name: Gerania

attacks.name: Adorno

attacks.name: Gigabatidora
